data.description: Discover unparalleled charm in this meticulously updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven, nestled on a scenic corner lot. Every inch of this home exudes sophistication and warmth, making it a truly one-of-a-kind opportunity. Immerse yourself in culinary delights with the sleek white shaker cabinets, crowned with marble countertops, and adorned with stainless steel appliances, including a counter-depth refrigerator. It's a chef's dream come true! Indulge in spa-like luxury within the newly renovated bathrooms, boasting modern fixtures and a touch of opulence at every turn. Hardwood floors cascade underfoot, leading you through sunlit spaces adorned with brand-new windows, fresh paint, and plush carpeting. The attention to detail is unparalleled.  Step into your private backyard retreat, surrounded by a new cedar fence that ensures tranquility and privacy. Perfect for entertaining or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars. Embrace the convenience of being across from the picturesque McCollum Park, offering endless recreational possibilities. With downtown Downers Grove just minutes away and easy access to major highways 355 & 55, restaurants, grocery stores and shopping - every adventure is within reach.  With every inch meticulously remodeled and cared for, this home is ready to welcome you with open arms. Simply unpack and start creating cherished memories. Listing agent has a vested interest in the property. *SELLER IS OPEN TO CONSIDERING A CREDIT OR REPAIR AS A POTENTIAL RESOLUTION TO ADDRESS ANY APPREHENSIONS THE BUYER MAY HAVE REGARDING THE CONDITION OF THE HOME, PARTICULARLY WITH RESPECT TO THE HARDWOOD FLOORS.
